{"tid":971913,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[投資比卡超]港美市場電力股投資比較","createTime":"2019-01-07T04:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T02:10:24.000Z","uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e1643717be3b506ad91e143808f08c5b9ac3849","tid":971913,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcDOYfC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcDOYfC.png&h=34f72ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖<br />\n冷色為港股 2638 2 6<br />\n暖色為美股 NEE DUK D EXC AEP PEG XEL DTE CNP<br />\n黑灰為指數ETF用作比較 2800 DIA<br />\n<br />\n就算經濟點差都好電力都係必須品, 而每個新科技產品誕生都必須應用電力<br />\n支那經濟出現重大問題, 全國衰退, 唯獨電力需求今年預測都要升7%, 無錯D廠走哂都要升<br />\n咁係未應該投資大陸既電力股? 錯! 大錯特錯, 能量電力呢類股票唔應該投資係一個封閉市場<br />\n因為能量電力等等既公司都係國家既, 為左配合國家發展係唔會有咩利潤, 唔信既你去睇支股市場任何一隻電力股, 係唔會搵倒一隻值得投資<br />\n<br />\n上圖既股點搵出黎, 只係有以下條件, 我先當佢做緊生意<br />\n5年月K圖有平均上升<br />\n市值700億港元或100億美元<br />\n派息2%以上<br />\nPE 30 以下<br />\n<br />\n乜大陸咁大真係冇隻滿足咁撚柒簡單既條件咩? 個國家真係好撚垃圾, 得一隻 600900.SH<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cd2ab322c72ff27ae68f85c2eeb3b8eb632380","tid":971913,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"PG&amp;E山火賠到破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b56bd04df846581d722f49dac69152b61d4f1d","tid":971913,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"我再將以上條件既比卡超, 加多個條件<br />\n5年內股價上升50%以上<br />\n就會得反 XEL NEE DTE 2638 EXC AEP PEG<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLbT9xB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLbT9xB.png&h=a5923dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4105b65108df9f8bcb8c86b531d63b83919519","tid":971913,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:43:52.000Z","ms